frames.caption: A giant, ethereal elephant with glowing purple eyes and flames emerges from a vibrant sunset sky. A solitary figure stands in a field of tall grass, gazing up at the majestic creature. The scene is both mystical and awe-inspiring, blending elements of fantasy and nature.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal encounter between a human and a colossal, otherworldly elephant engulfed in purple flames. The setting is a vast savannah at sunset, with dramatic lighting enhancing the mystical atmosphere.
